Type Definitions

testCallback(page, data, assert)

This callback is executed as a test and will only be run when any previous test has completed. If Setup and TearDown methods are specified in the test options those will be run before and after the test
Parameters:
Name Type Description
page PhantomJs.Webpage.Page a PhantomJs Page object for use in testing
data Object the data object passed to the PFT.tester.test function
assert PFT.tester.assert a convenience object for accessing PFT.tester.assert
